#Text=2. Theoretical Analysis of MCR-WPT System with Intermediate Coils

#Text=2.2. Equivalent Circuit Model of a Two-Intermediate Coil WPT System
#Text=Two intermediate coils have the short circuit topology .
#Text=The transmission distance is longer owing to using two-intermediate coils with a high quality factor .
